Question: Do you think Facebook enhance quality of life? Motivate your answer.
Answer:
I do think that Facebook has the potential to enhance quality of life. It has an interface that allows a person to easily connect with the persons they care about. I also think that there is an inherent problem with facebook. People can become enamored with the attention they receive on facebook and consequently spend more time than they should on it. At this point in time, I think the risk outweighs the potential.